GNU Make Standard Library
-------------------------

1. Visit http://gmsl.sf.net for more details

2. To use the GMSL in your Makefile make sure that you have the files

   gmsl
   __gmsl

   Add 

   include gmsl

   to your Makefile(s).

3. To run the GMSL test suite have 

   gmsl
   __gmsl
   gmsl-tests

   And then run

   make -f gmsl-tests

 